list.abstract: Team（英[tiːm]，美[tiːm]），英文单词，作名词为队；组；班等。作动词为结成一队；协作；配合等。短语搭配有team spirit（团队精神；合作精神；团结精神）。例句为“Work in a team for six months.（在团队中工作六个月。）”。 该单词的复数形式为teams，名词类近义词为group、crew、suit，及物动词类近义词为partner，不及物动词类近义词为work together、co-operate。

Team是一首由新西兰才女Lorde于2013年9月13日创作的专辑《Pure Heroine》中的第三首单曲。 team 是专辑《纯粹女英雄》的第六首歌，这首歌为我们描绘了一个充满魔幻色彩的世界，也就是歌曲《Royals》说let me live that fantasy里的fantasy world。对于这首歌的mv，据lorde的说法，是她有天梦到一个属于青少年自己的世界，在那里面是有等级制度的，而且有入会仪式。在那里，男孩的权力没有女孩大，女孩在那里都是女王。在这个世界里，到处长满热带植物，又很潮湿，而且是一个废墟。lorde说其实入会仪式并不需要别人的同意，只要是所谓的失败者都能进入。在那里失败的人最强大。

yingyinNormal.en: I've already put together my team.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我已经组织了团队。

yingyinNormal.en: And Paul's team brought the mathematics to life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而保罗的团队将该数学运算变成了现实。

yingyinNormal.en: What if we disguised a new team to look like the old team? Oh, no, no. We are not cheating.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要是我们偷天换日，伪装得像旧团队？不行，我们不能作弊

yingyinNormal.en: Your men are shot to shit. What are you gonna do for a team?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的人伤得不轻，你要怎么组建团队？

yingyinNormal.en: That's his MO, isn't it? I mean, what are we, a team?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是他的管理方法，我们算什么？一个团队？

yingyinNormal.en: We can try. No. My team will take over the investigation now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们可以试试。不行，现在由我的团队接手调查。

yingyinNormal.en: So you're going for artificial intelligence and you don't want to tell the team?
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以你要研究人工智能，还不想告诉团队？

yingyinNormal.en: It's about being a team and sticking together, no matter what!
yingyinNormal.zh: 作为一个团队无论发生什么事情，我们应该一直团结在一起！
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge Out of Water》

yingyinNormal.en: It was a team effort. Who is your source? I can't. You know that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是团队合作的成果，是谁告诉你的？我不能透露，你懂的。

yingyinNormal.en: As head of this team, and I think I speak for everyone, we have done…
yingyinNormal.zh: 作为团队领袖，我认为我可以代表所有人说我们已经...

yingyinNormal.en: Tell the creative team to get their giggles out. I'll be ready for them in 10.
yingyinNormal.zh: 让创意团队别嬉皮笑脸了，我十分钟后就能见他们。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh My Gosh. Duke find our lost ball. What a great team we're gonna be.
yingyinNormal.zh: 天呐，杜克找到我们丢的球了，我们一定会成为最佳团队。

yingyinNormal.en: Maybe they're not your friends. That was my whole point about team today.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也许他们不是你真正的朋友。这也就是我说的团队合作。

yingyinNormal.en: I assumed you might say that. Which is why I've taken the liberty of gathering your team.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我就知道你会这么说，所以我擅自集合了你的团队。

yingyinNormal.en: And I can work with the political team, coordinate with House leg directors, chiefs of staff.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我能配合政治团队协调，国会立法主任和幕僚长。

yingyinNormal.en: Amy, I was off by a factor of 10,000. But the Chinese team found the element.
yingyinNormal.zh: Amy 我算差了十万八千里，但中国团队发现了那个元素。

yingyinNormal.en: For the past five months, my team has sat at this very table, developing America Works.
yingyinNormal.zh: 过去五个月，我的团队就坐在这儿，起草美国就业法案。

yingyinNormal.en: We? But even failure hurts a little less when you do it as a team, right?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们？但当你身处团队中时即使失败也不觉得那么沮丧了，不是吗？
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge Out of Water》

yingyinNormal.en: Every time your team rolls out an update, there's a possibility of a critical failure.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每次你的团队运行一次更新，都有出现重大故障的可能性。

yingyinNormal.en: Your team? Are you kidding me? Look, this guy couldn't debug a balled-up napkin.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的团队？你开玩笑吗？听着，这家伙连个揉成团的纸巾都打不开。
